data.description: Brand new manufactured home situated on a nice sized lot with great curb appeal, decks, and off-street parking. These homes are all amazing. As you enter you are greeted with a large living room with carpet. The eat-in kitchen features a center island, and stainless appliances and overlooks the living room. The master bedroom has 3/4 attached bath with a walk-in closet. This 4 bedroom unit has additional bedrooms off the main hallway with a full bathroom and laundry. The laundry room walks out to the side entry as well. Maintance-free exterior includes vinyl siding, Trex decking, and metal handrails. The home is completely electric for ease. Located close to Pueblo Blvd, 24th street, parks, and more. In an unaffordable time, we have an affordable home for you!
